@startuml
actor Pembeli
participant View
participant Controller
participant EkspedisiAPI
participant Model
participant Database

Pembeli -> View : Pilih item di keranjang\nKlik "Checkout"
View -> Controller : GET /checkout
Controller -> Model : get selected cart items
Model -> Database : query
Database --> Model : results
Model --> Controller : results
Controller --> View : Return halaman Checkout
View --> Pembeli : Tampilkan halaman Checkout (Ringkasan)

Pembeli -> View : Pilih/Masukkan alamat pengiriman
View -> Controller : POST /checkout/ongkir (alamat)
Controller -> EkspedisiAPI : get_shipping_options(origin, dest, weight)
EkspedisiAPI --> Controller : return options & cost
Controller --> View : Return opsi kurir & ongkos
View --> Pembeli : Tampilkan opsi kurir & ongkos kirim

Pembeli -> View : Pilih kurir/layanan pengiriman
View -> Controller : POST /checkout/courier (pilihan)
Controller -> Controller : Hitung total (Harga + Ongkir)
Controller --> View : Return total & opsi pembayaran
View --> Pembeli : Tampilkan total akhir & opsi pembayaran

Pembeli -> View : Pilih metode pembayaran\nKonfirmasi Checkout
View -> Controller : POST /checkout/process (data pesanan)
Controller -> Model : create_order(data)
Model -> Database : insert order & order_items
Database --> Model : success
Model --> Controller : success
Controller -> Controller : Set status "Menunggu Pembayaran"
Controller -> Controller : Kirim notifikasi pembayaran
Controller --> View : Redirect to payment page
View --> Pembeli : Tampilkan instruksi pembayaran
@enduml
